opendsme - opensource dsme replacement
http://git.slonopotamus.org/?p=opendsme

Dependencies
------------
CMake >= 2.6 is required to build from sources.
popt is required at build and runtime for command-line args processing.

Compiling
---------
See the INSTALL document for build instructions.

Documentation
-------------
See -h output of programs contained in opendsme package.

